     H            Y.
     F** UTLR77 ***********************************************
     F*  PROGRAM: FORD - GET PLANT CODE (BY DELV#/DOCK)       *
     F*  WRITTEN: JW (SRA) 2020.01.22                         *
     F*-------------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UTLR77'
     F*                    PARM           $DLV    4
     F*                    PARM           $FACT   1
     F*                    PARM           $DOCK   4
     F*                    PARM           $PLANT 10
     F*                    PARM           $RTN    1
     F*  IN  $DLV  :  4A DELIVERY#
     F*      $FACT :  1A FACTORY
     F*      $DOCK :  4A DOCK
     F*  OUT $PLANT: 10A PLANT CODE
     F*      $RTN  :  1A RETURN CODE (BLANK/*)
     F******************************************************
     FABFDL05 IF  E           K        DISK
      *===================================================
      *           MAIN ROUTINE
      *===================================================
     C                     EXSR #INIT
      * FORD
     C           @NONY     SETLLABFDL05
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C           @NONY     READEABFDL05                  98
     C   98                LEAVE
      *
     C           QADOCK    IFEQ $DOCK
     C                     MOVELQAPLAN    $PLANT    P
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           QADOCK    IFEQ *BLANK
     C           QADOCK    OREQ '0   '
     C           QADOCK    OREQ '00  '
     C                     MOVELQAPLAN    $PLANT    P
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVELQAPLAN    XPLANT    P
      *
     C                     ENDDO
      * DEFAULT
     C           $PLANT    IFEQ *BLANK
     C           XPLANT    ANDNE*BLANK
     C                     MOVELXPLANT    $PLANT
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           $PLANT    IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVE '*'       $RTN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *======================================================
      * INITIAL SET
      *======================================================
     C           #INIT     BEGSR
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $DLV    4
     C                     PARM           $FACT   1
     C                     PARM           $DOCK   4
     C                     PARM           $PLANT 10
     C                     PARM           $RTN    1
      *
     C                     MOVEL$DLV      @NONY   40
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $PLANT
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    XPLANT 10
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $RTN
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *====================================================
